title: Became King After Being Bitten
description: Became King After Being Bitten After rebirth, the world has changed. The blood clan has become the master of the world, and mankind has fully accepted this life and is proud to be a family member of the blood clan. As the saying goes : humans who have not been sucked by the blood clan are not good people. Wang Zhe wanted to repair the regrets left in his previous life and live a better life, but unexpectedly, he was involved in all kinds of events competing for the quota of blood family members. At the critical moment of life and death, a mysterious force in Wang Zhe’s body revived. The blood families, real masters and real kings came! Less… Become King After Being Bitten Becoming King After Being Bitten Bei Yao Hou Chengwei Wangzhe Bèi Yǎo Hòu Chéngwéi Wángzhě Make Me the Vampire King! 被咬后成为王者
